algorithms

Class FixedSizeVector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.FixedSizeVector<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - class type to be held and sorted by this class. It must implement Comparable.

    public class FixedSizeVector<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    a class to hold a fixed number of items of type T. The latest capacity number of items are what is present in the vector. 
     runtime complexity is:
     O(1) for inserts, and gets
 Note that deletes are not allowed,
    but could be implemented in O(N) runtime.
 
 where N is the fixed capacity.
    Author:
    nichole
